sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant FS as File Storage

    U->>API: GET /api/batches/{batch_id}
    API->>API: Extract device fingerprint
    API->>DB: Find User by fingerprint
    DB-->>API: User record
    
    API->>DB: Find ScanBatch WHERE id = ? AND user_id = ?
    
    alt Batch not found or unauthorized
        DB-->>API: null
        API-->>U: 404 Not Found
    else Batch found
        DB-->>API: ScanBatch record
        API->>DB: Find ScanImages WHERE batch_id = ?
        DB-->>API: Images list
        API->>DB: Find SeedDetections WHERE batch_id = ?
        DB-->>API: Detections list
        API-->>U: { batch: {...}, images: [...], detections: [...] }
    end

    Note over U,API: Optional: Retrieve actual image file
    U->>API: GET /api/images/{batch_id}/{filename}
    API->>FS: Read file
    FS-->>API: Image bytes
    API-->>U: Image file (binary)
